        "description": "The most comprehensive SOQL query filter builder in NPSP, supporting the full range of WHERE clause conditions with chainable methods, and also capable of re-evaluating those same filters in Apex memory against a list of records without issuing an additional query. The source code Provides runtime filtering via `UTIL_Where.filter(List<sObject>)`, which re-evaluates the WHERE clause criteria in Apex memory against a list of SObjects without issuing a SOQL query. This is used by `UTIL_Finder` when SOSL results need post-filtering. The `isFilterable()` propagation detects encrypted fields (`Schema.DisplayType.EncryptedString`) in the field expressions and marks the entire WHERE clause as non-filterable, preventing SOSL execution that would fail on encrypted fields."
