        "description": "Custom Settings object that stores configurable naming formats for donation records. Each record specifies a name format template using `{!FieldName}` syntax to reference any donation or related record field, a date format using Java SimpleDateFormat syntax, an attribution type (Contact donations, Organization donations, or both), and which record types the format applies to (blank means all types). The default naming convention produces names like \"Barnaby Jones Donation 12/12/21.\" When settings change, the new naming convention applies only to newly created donations; existing records require a bulk refresh process to be renamed.",
