        "description": "Captures timing metrics for each stage of the BDI import pipeline, helping diagnose performance bottlenecks in large-volume import operations. It creates named log entries for individual processing steps so you can see exactly which stage took the most time when investigating a slow import. The source code This performance logging utility extends `UTIL_PerfLogger` to add a `BDI_Batch__c` context field on all log entries, allowing BDI batch performance data to be filtered and analyzed independently of other NPSP performance logs. Each stage of `BDI_DataImportService.process()` creates a named `PerfLog` instance, stops it after the stage completes, and the resulting timing data is available for DML into a custom performance log object."
