        "description": "Lightning Web Component that provides the primary Relationships Viewer interface on Contact record pages, showing how a Contact is connected to others as an interactive visual map. It supports expanding to second- and third-level relationship networks so you can explore your constituents' broader social and professional circles. Administrators add it to Contact Lightning Record Pages by dragging the Relationships Navigator component onto the layout in the Lightning App Builder. Each connection displays its relationship Type (e.g., Spouse, Parent, Employer) and Status indicator.",
