        "description": "Custom object that serves as a lightweight progress-tracking container for grouping records during bulk data operations. It stores the batch's current status, a description of what the batch is doing, the count of items being processed, and the target object the batch is operating against. Used in NPSP's legacy batch processing workflows to monitor and manage the progress of bulk record operations. Because it acts as a status tracking record rather than a data store, it uses a public read/write sharing model so any running batch job or monitoring user can read and update it without ownership restrictions.",
